ygData.subject: RE: Am I missing something? Does the aqualung.. um .. Suck?
ygData.msgSnippet: No, I don t think it sucks at all. Aqualung.  50 charges.  Not bad.  Is there anything else in the game with this many charges? Rebreather - unlimited.  Now,
ygData.messageBody:
No, I don't think it sucks at all.

Aqualung. 50 charges. Not bad. Is there anything else in
the game with this many charges?

Rebreather - unlimited. Now, how much have you seen the
Fishbone earring sell for? Eh? Oh, NO ONE is selling them? Oh, Trade
ONLY? Hehehehe, well, now we can make an item that EVERYONE will want if
they want to go to Kedge Keep. Yes yes yes, it weighs 10. Small price to
pay instead of camping a 6 hour spawn with a rare drop.

Just my 2 cents. I for one am happy tinkering finally has
some kewl stuff to make. Now if only they would put back in the Jet Pack,
and the pet rat/spider/gnome.

On another note, what the heck does the gemcutter do?
